blic sphere in Europe.  afunded by Carlsberg Foundation  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aAufgeklärter Absolutismus. 4aDänemark. 4aMeinungsfreiheit. 4aStruensee, Johann Friedrich von. 7aHISTORY / Modern / General.2bisacsh  aDenmark.  aFreedom of expression.  aStruensee, Johann Friedrich von.  aenligthened absolutism.1 aStjernfelt, Frederik, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut2 aCarlsberg Foundationefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishz978311099296008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022z9783110992939oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831107718620 cprintz978311077123740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110771800zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110771800zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110771800/original  a978-3-11-099296-0 EBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-GOA